    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This mean in Hebrew, the Smart Yeshiva in Lublin-- in English.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this built in 1928, they built the yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] and make like and built this in the same, like, in Israel, 2,000 years ago, in the [INAUDIBLE], by [INAUDIBLE].",
